728633f-a.title: Richmond: Canal Street - Front Street
728633f-a.text:
47 Canal Street, north side, between Front and Bay Streets
(Stapleton), near the Staten lIsland Railroad crossing, showing a
branch shelter of the American Society for the Prevention of Cruelty
to Animals.
May 1, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
